citation: Proclamation under the Medical Radiation Science Professionals Registration Act 2000 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Medical Radiation Science Professionals Registration Act 2000

I, the Governor in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Medical Radiation Science Professionals Registration Act 2000 fix 1 July 2002 as the day on which that Act commences.

4 June 2002

G. S. M. Green

Governor

By His Excellency's Command,

Judy Jackson

Minister for Health and Human Services

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 12 June 2002

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Health and Human Services.
